<p>
  Reports unclosed heredoc delimiters at the end of the file.
</p>
<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
This code will report missing FILE2 and FILE3 delimiters.
<pre><code>
  RUN &lt;&lt;FILE1 cat &gt; file1 && &lt;&lt;FILE2 cat &gt; file2 && &lt;&lt;FILE3 cat &gt; file3
  mkdir -p foo/bar
  FILE1
</code></pre>
